# Dynamic Blog Website

A fully functional dynamic blog website built with PHP and MySQL during my internship.

## Features

- User Registration & Login
- Secure Password Hashing
- User Logout
- Add New Blog Posts
- Image Upload with Posts
- View All Blog Posts
- View Individual Post Details
- Category System (Quran, Hadith, Dua)
- Search Functionality
- Fully Responsive Design

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Bootstrap
- PHP
- MySQL

## Setup Instructions

1. Download and install XAMPP
2. Clone this repository into `htdocs` folder
3. Import `database.sql` file into phpMyAdmin
4. Start Apache and MySQL in XAMPP
5. Open browser and go to `localhost/your-folder-name`

## Database

Import the included `.sql` file to set up the database automatically.

## Security

- Prepared statements used for all database queries
- Passwords are hashed using PHP `password_hash()`

